pg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1aX29y.jpg&h=1cd4a35c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/142018_a46ee706141d219ff409bbd9e1cc60e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F142018_a46ee706141d219ff409bbd9e1cc60e5.jpg&h=beba5dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nA7SR3q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnA7SR3q.gif&h=507bf8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">玻璃貼</span>:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/141236_57aaf9e46839434429731493743a0afc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F141236_57aaf9e46839434429731493743a0afc.jpg&h=a917ed3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/221040_6630f7298dc9b31061ab33f1d6aaf027.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F221040_6630f7298dc9b31061ab33f1d6aaf027.jpg&h=92093784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nS10超聲波指紋適用<br />\n<br />\nwhitestone dome<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobilefun.com/whitestone-dome-glass-samsung-galaxy-s10-screen-protector-2-pack-70996\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobilefun.com%2Fwhitestone-dome-glass-samsung-galaxy-s10-screen-protector-2-pack-70996&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=80a93b4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobilefun.com/whitestone-dome-glass-samsung-galaxy-s10-screen-protector-2-pack-70996</a><br />\n<br />\n淘寶官方link S10貼已上架<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.whitestonedome.com/blog/taobao-customers-review-in-taobao-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitestonedome.com%2Fblog%2Ftaobao-customers-review-in-taobao-china%2F&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=7fc3f61b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.whitestonedome.com/blog/taobao-customers-review-in-taobao-china/</a><br />\n<br />\nSmart Octopus<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCAHotc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCAHotc.gif&h=0cd5fc8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSamsung Galaxy 集中討論區 ( 54 )<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1308218/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1308218/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[親身fact check] 有需要過羅湖手足必須del 遊行相<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394611\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394611</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n用三叔機既<br />\n要上大陸/發夢既就將d相/tg放入安全資料夾<br />\n就咁開正常相薄係睇唔到安全資料夾入面所有資料<br />\n然後hide埋個安全資料夾個app 完美<br />\n<br />\n各位請保護自己<br />\n<br />\n安全資料夾利用國防級的 Samsung Knox 安全平台，在您的三星手機上打造一個私人的加密空間。移至安全資料夾的應用程序和數據在設備中處於隔離的沙箱中，可獲得額外的安全性和私密性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n※ 安全文件夾是基於三星帳戶的服務，它可在您的移動設備中打造一個獨立的隔離環境。移動或添加至安全文件夾的應用程序和數據 (例如照片、音頻文件、電影文件和文檔) 將無法從安全文件夾外部訪問，<span style=\"color: red;\">無論是 USB 還是 Wi-Fi 直連都不可以。</span>如果您的移動設備檢測到任何Root 權限獲取或ROM 自定義操作，為防止未授權的訪問，安全文件夾將自動鎖定，在這種情況下，您將無法再訪問或使用安全文件夾中的內容。因此，在將應用程序或數據移至安全文件夾之前，請務必在個人電腦等其他位置備份所有重要的應用程序或數據。三星對任何數據丟失或無法訪問概不負責。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安全資料夾教學<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dVPvSOleYxU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdVPvSOleYxU&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=c3c2b756\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dVPvSOleYxU</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8100c7v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8100c7v.jpg&h=31222d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>用Samsung手機既可以簡單地將手機畫面拍成gif<br />\n方便大家將消息傳開</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F8NsCP0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8NsCP0.png&h=f0a2c077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUcL8Ww.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUcL8Ww.png&h=4fbd84fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iOn4E3a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiOn4E3a.png&h=baeb9f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tYQ9Rae.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtYQ9Rae.gif&h=dbbb3ae0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3fbc76fcd95057906dd3e1eac6f29399b8a57e0","tid":1516033,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/29/201427_840b38ab75d847b3fc0549aa28c937d1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F29%2F201427_840b38ab75d847b3fc0549aa28c937d1.JPG&h=011f4847&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f891ec9b15557468b1b3fceca0c7bf42ceb179bd","tid":1516033,"uid":92477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b3fbc76fcd95057906dd3e1eac6f29399b8a57e0","tid":1516033,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/29/201427_840b38ab75d847b3fc0549aa28c937d1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F29%2F201427_840b38ab75d847b3fc0549aa28c937d1.JPG&h=011f4847&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":